products.title: Spirit Mulberry Venetian Blind - 25mm Slat
products.description: The spirit mulberry aluminium venetian blind is light, gorgeous and an elegant choice if you're looking to add a bit of colour to your home. This blind will give your home a most delectable and tranquil setting both day and night. The smooth matte slats are also easy to clean, the spirit mulberry aluminium venetian blind is light, gorgeous and an elegant choice if you're looking to add a bit of colour to your home.
